  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Women with disseminated breast cancer, HER-2 3+ or FISH+.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Women older than 18.

          2. Patients with disseminated breast cancer with overexpression of HER-2 (IHC 3 + or FISH
             +).

          3. Patients who have been treated with trastuzumab (Herceptin ®).

          4. Complete remission, partial or stable disease for a period exceeding 3 years, except
             for exclusive cerebral progression.

          5. Patients who have given their written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        1- Patients with remission achieved with surgery or less than three months of treatment
        with trastuzumab.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
